# 詞: 睇怕

1. 佢成日講大話，大家睇怕佢，唔敢同佢講真話。 (He always tells lies, so everyone is fed up with him and dares not tell him the truth.)
2. 呢個老闆成日無理由炒人，員工都睇怕佢，想走都走唔到。 (This boss fires people without reason all the time; the employees are fed up with him but feel trapped and can't leave.)
3. 我睇怕呢個劇本，成日改來改去，根本唔知點樣拍先至好。 (I'm fed up with this script; it keeps getting changed back and forth, and I don't know how to film it properly.)
4. 佢個女朋友成日無端端發脾氣，佢都睇怕佢，想分手又唔捨得。 (His girlfriend throws tantrums for no reason all the time; he's fed up with her but wants to break up yet can't bear to do it.)
5. 呢個遊戲成日出 Bug，玩家都睇怕佢，唔想再玩落去。 (This game keeps having bugs; the players are fed up with it and don't want to play anymore.)
6. 我睇怕呢個天氣，成日落雨，出街都唔方便。 (I'm fed up with this weather; it rains all the time, making it inconvenient to go out.)
7. 佢個老闆成日加鐘，員工都睇怕佢，想轉工都無地方去。 (His boss keeps adding overtime hours; the employees are fed up with him and want to change jobs but have nowhere to go.)
8. 我睇怕呢個新聞，成日講啲負面嘢，聽完心情好差。 (I'm fed up with this news; it always talks about negative things, and I feel terrible after hearing it.)
9. 佢個鄰居成日嘈吵，我睇怕佢，想搬屋都無錢。 (His neighbor is noisy all the time; I'm fed up with him and want to move but don't have the money.)
10. 我睇怕呢個工作，成日加班，無時間陪家人。 (I'm fed up with this job; I have to work overtime all the time and have no time to spend with my family.) [end of text]


